summary: My Message to Dan and Phil
body:
My Message to Dan and Phil

**UPDATED**

For Dan and Phil:

Hi, my name is Halli Judd, I am 17 years old. I live in St. George, Utah and I have aspergers. I want to tell you guys about how you have changed my life for the better. It all started in 2017, that year was a real blur for me. I had problems with my self esteem and have suffered from depression after (and maybe during) a manipulative friendship with some boy as well as having self harm thoughts because of him. Then near the end of October 2017 is when I’ve heard my best friend talk about you guys and she said your videos are the best. I figured I should probably check them out. November 2017 is when I started watching your videos and ever since then my life has changed forever. And the trauma I’ve dealt with before had melted away. I really want to thank you guys for all you’ve done for me, and I really appreciate it. Not just me, but to everyone else who loves you too. You have helped me out so much! You guys are amazing! And the night I went to Interactive Introverts was the best experience of my life! I don’t know what I would’ve done without you guys. You have saved my life, and I will never forget that. And I will never give you guys up. I love you guys so much! And you guys are the reason why my 2018 turned out better and I can’t wait to see what 2019 will bring!

PS, my bestie says ‘hi’ and she loves you guys too!

Anyways, thanks for reading and I love you guys❤️

>•<
